      • Review

        public Review​(int rating,
              java.lang.String comment,
              java.lang.String userID)
        Constructor of Review object. Requires rating, and comments given by customer, and unique customer ID of customer who left the review. Every new review will also increment counter for ReviewID ensuring that each review has an unique ID.
        Parameters:
        rating - Rating left by customer, integer value out of 10.
        comment - Comment left by customer on movie
        userID - Unique ID of customer who left the review
